cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CL

The paper focuses on event detection in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of pre-trained concept classifiers and the exploration of online available videos with free-form text descriptions suggest a machine learning approach (cs.LG). The proposed method involves combining multiple prediction score vectors, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM). The use of text descriptions also suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as possible sub-categories.
